27d900a0-f7e5-4dfb-8c51-a524800945be.name: ucp_pool_name
27d900a0-f7e5-4dfb-8c51-a524800945be.queryValue:
SELECT distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'pool.name') 
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4
WHERE (metric_name = 'db.client.connections.usage') 
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'service.name') in {{.app_name}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'host.name') in {{.instance}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'pool.name') != '')

6700d7f0-fd97-46c8-8a95-34c2336cf760.name: app_name
6700d7f0-fd97-46c8-8a95-34c2336cf760.queryValue:
SELECT distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'application')
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4
WHERE (metric_name = 'jvm_memory_used_bytes')
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'application') != '')

8a781896-9103-4bf4-8827-382adc58a139.name: memory_pool_heap
8a781896-9103-4bf4-8827-382adc58a139.queryValue:
SELECT distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'id') 
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4
WHERE (metric_name = 'jvm_memory_used_bytes') 
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'area') = 'heap') 
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'application') in {{.app_name}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.namespace.name') in {{.namespace}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.pod.name') in {{.instance}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'id') != '')

911449fe-20f1-43f9-847a-b041d6f6cab5.name: memory_pool_non_heap
911449fe-20f1-43f9-847a-b041d6f6cab5.queryValue:
SELECT distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'id') 
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4
WHERE (metric_name = 'jvm_memory_used_bytes') 
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'area') = 'nonheap') 
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'application') in {{.app_name}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.namespace.name') in {{.namespace}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.pod.name') in {{.instance}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'id') != '')

d36224de-16d4-4782-9b90-ca5ce803b864.name: namespace
d36224de-16d4-4782-9b90-ca5ce803b864.queryValue:
SELECT distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.namespace.name') 
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4
WHERE (metric_name = 'jvm_memory_used_bytes')
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'application') in {{.app_name}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.namespace.name') != '')

ecbce4d2-8c43-4d33-af0c-a29c06b5c60b.name: instance
ecbce4d2-8c43-4d33-af0c-a29c06b5c60b.queryValue:
SELECT distinct JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.pod.name') 
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4
WHERE (metric_name = 'jvm_memory_used_bytes')
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.namespace.name') in {{.namespace}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'application') in {{.app_name}})
and (JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s.pod.name') != '')
